Package: offline-lab-archive-keyring
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: GnuPG archive keys for the Offline Lab package repository
 The Offline Lab project signs its Release files. This package
 contains the archive key used for that, along with the apt sources
 configuration for repo.offline-lab.com.
